  "text": "Ξ is a diagonal matrix where the i-th diagonal entry ξ i is the stationary state distribution w.r.t state s i . and L = I −γP . However, L −1 is also computationally prohibitive. To this end, a more practical way is to compute a Galerkin-Bubnov approximate solution [CITATION_1] is via solving a fixed-point",
